pt-5 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-300\">Open tool</span></a><a class=\"group flex min-h-56 flex-col rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/mp3-cutter\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-blue-300\">Audio Tools</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">MP3 Cutter</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-400\">Trim MP3 audio by start and end time in your browser and export WAV.</p><span class=\"mt-auto pt-5 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-300\">Open tool</span></a><a class=\"group flex min-h-56 flex-col rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/change-audio-volume\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-blue-300\">Audio Tools</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Change Audio Volume</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-400\">Adjust MP3, WAV, OGG or M4A volume in your browser and export WAV audio.</p><span class=\"mt-auto pt-5 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-300\">Open tool</span></a><a class=\"group flex min-h-56 flex-col rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 transition hover:border-blue-500/60 hover:bg-slate-900\" href=\"/convert/audio-converter\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase text-blue-300\">Audio Tools</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold\">Convert Audio to WAV</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-400\">Convert MP3, WAV, OGG or M4A audio to WAV in your browser.</p><span class=\"mt-auto pt-5 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-300\">Open tool</span></a></div></section><section class=\"px-6 pb-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl\"><aside class=\"rounded-2xl border border-amber-400/20 bg-amber-400/5 p-6\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase text-amber-200\">Sponsored</p><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-white\">Featured software partner</h3><p class=\"mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-400\">A reserved placement for a relevant file, productivity or document software partner.</p><a class=\"mt-5 inline-flex text-sm font-semibold text-amber-200 hover:text-amber-100\" href=\"/partners\">Explore partnership options</a></aside></div></section><section class=\"border-y border-white/10 bg-slate-900/40 px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black\">Why use these tools?</h2><div class=\"mt-6 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2\"><p class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-6 leading-7 text-slate-300\">Make quick audio changes without a full desktop audio editor.</p><p class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 p-6 leading-7 text-slate-300\">Receive clearly labelled WAV output when browser-native MP3 encoding is not dependable.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"px-6 py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black\">Frequently asked questions</h2><div class=\"mt-8 space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">Which audio formats are supported?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-400\">Tools accept combinations of MP3, WAV, OGG and M4A depending on browser decoding support.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">Why is the download sometimes WAV?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-400\">WAV is the reliable client-side export format used when MP3 encoding would require a heavier dependency.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold\">Does audio leave my device?</h3><p class=\"mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-400\">Audio decoding and processing run in your browser.</p></div></div><h2 class=\"mt-16 text-2xl font-black\">Explore other categories</h2><div class=\"mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-200 hover:border-blue-500/60\" href=\"/image-tools\">Image Tools</a><a class=\"roun